  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "After translating the individual sentences with the fine-tuned NLLB, the outputs are not coherent as they are translated in isolation.",
    "Moreover, any ASR errors that might be fixed by observing the full document will be translated incorrectly.",
    "To mitigate this, we perform an additional step of documentlevel automatic post-editing using the source transcripts and sentence translations shown in Figure 2.",
    "Similar to the situation outlined in Section 3.2, we encountered a lack of data for fine-tuning the LLM for document-level post-editing.",
    "Hence, we adopted the approach proposed by Koneru et al. (2023) to create the dataset."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "Hence, we adopted the approach proposed by Koneru et al. (2023) to create the dataset."
  ]
}